    <tr>

      <td><img src="images-layout/portalone.png" style="width:100%;max-width:250px;"  alt=""/>

        <h2>Ring Compressors / Regenerative Blowers</h2><p>

The Fuji Ring Compressor is a non-positive displacement, high volume, low pressure blower that can operate as either a compressor or a vacuum pump.  It is also known as: Fuji regenerative blower, vortex blower and side-channel blower.  All ring compressor impellers are dynamically balanced to virtually eliminate vibration while increasing overall long-term reliability.  <br>

<a href="ring-compressors-regenerative-blowers.shtml">More on Ring Compressors »</a></p></td>

    </tr>

  </tbody>

</table>



