        <h2>Vacuum Systems</h2><p>

Cary Manufacturing provides a full line of products geared to the removal of waste in various critical areas of the production process.  Our line of industrial vacuum cleaners includes a variety of hi-performance, industrial vacs in a range of sizes designed to fit your particular needs.  One such product is the Cary Vac industrial vacuum cleaner.  <br>

<a href="vacuum-systems.shtml">More on Vacuum Systems »</a></p></td>

    </tr>

